---
import ScrollingText from './me/scrolling-text.astro'
---

<section
  aria-label="about me"
  class="flex h-screen snap-start flex-col justify-center border-b-2 border-black bg-white"
>
  <div
    class="flex h-screen flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 p-8 md:items-start md:gap-6 md:px-32"
  >
    <div
      class="mb-2 rounded-3xl border-[3px] border-b-8 border-r-4 border-black bg-white px-12 py-4"
    >
      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-3xl">Hello there! üòÅ</h2>
    </div>

    <p
      class="text-md flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-orange-100 px-3 py-2 text-[#605574] md:text-xl"
    >
      I'm Daniel, a Software Engineer from Brazil
      <img class="hidden md:block" src="brazil.svg" alt="brazil flag" />
    </p>

    <p
      class="text-md rounded-md bg-orange-100 px-3 py-2 text-[#605574] md:text-xl"
    >
      I do mostly web dev related stuff.
    </p>

    <p
      class="text-md rounded-md bg-orange-100 px-3 py-2 text-[#605574] md:text-xl"
    >
      I'm usually working with frontend and backend, and sometimes I do some DB
      things as well.
    </p>

    <p
      class="text-md rounded-md bg-orange-100 px-3 py-2 text-[#605574] md:text-xl"
    >
      Recently, I have been captivated by the world of UI/UX design...
    </p>

    <p
      class="text-md rounded-md bg-orange-100 px-3 py-2 text-[#605574] md:text-xl"
    >
      ... and have been delving deeper into the subject.
    </p>

    <p
      class="text-md rounded-md bg-orange-100 px-3 py-2 text-[#605574] md:text-xl"
    >
      I instantly became a fan on the Neo Brutalism design when I first
      discovered that it was...
    </p>

    <p
      class="text-md rounded-md bg-orange-100 px-3 py-2 text-[#605574] md:text-xl"
    >
      ... being used by websites like <a
        class="underline"
        href="https://www.figma.com"
        target="_blank">Figma.com</a
      > and <a class="underline" href="https://prismic.io" target="_blank"
        >Prismic.io</a
      >.
    </p>

    <p
      class="text-md rounded-md bg-orange-100 px-3 py-2 text-[#605574] md:text-xl"
    >
      I'm very passionate about software development and I'd love to chat with
      you about it!
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="hidden md:block">
    <ScrollingText />
  </div>
</section>
